{
  "title": "gameboard-bot \u2014 Layered Architecture (merged)",
  "subtitle": "Game-agnostic engine seam (Game/Evaluator/Encoder) shared by WallChess + Checkers; UI/CLI/wasm on top, offline training below. Dashed = deferred / not-yet-wired.",
